message: "There's a lot of parents out there that will not necessarily let their kids go to the mall, or the movies because they're scared of danger. But they'll never think twice about handing them a phone, that allows access anywhere worldwide, to every predator out there," said Trooper Gossen.

data.description: A Louisiana mother's search for her son led authorities to another missing boy in Florida, and the discovery of an alleged sex trafficking ring.
